'''Tamahaq''' nɣ '''Tamahaɣt''' (Tinglizt: Tahaggart Tamahaq, Tamahaq Tahaggart) s waḍu nns ad igan tutlayt tatwargit tagafayt ittyusawaln ɣ [[Dzayr]], Ataram n [[Libya]] d ugafa n [[Nnijr|Nnijer]]. Mmzrint s imikk f tutlayin titwargiyin n ugmuḍ n idrarn Ayr, Azawaɣ d Adaɣ. Inuḥyuten ɣ umata gan win tsnmslit, zun d ''Tamahaq'' ɣ yida n ''Tamajaq'' nɣ ''Tamceq.''

== Timzarayin ==
